óŔQarchive/external_nushell_repo_backup/nushell.github.io/commands/docs/path_self.mdŔ@8d8e36d49fd7d720232b009cf7c15b37664a63b797da43c06bf35815c671c1c7įtitle: path selfĎ®ExamplesŕgGet the path of the current file.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> const current_file = path self


```
Get the path of the directory containing the current file.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> const current_file = path self .


```
Get the absolute form of a path relative to the current file.
```Fenced(Borrowed("nu"))
> const current_file = path self ../foo


```
